{"uuid": "ed81f9c4-90d5-4d43-bbe5-c09ed82a1ba6", "title": "Chat", "project": {"uuid": "7afb8304-e2e6-4db8-877f-af2c0b89d102", "name": "TalKo\u5e94\u7528\u56fe\u6807\u8bbe\u8ba1"}, "created_at": "2026-07-04T13:46:15.989336+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-07-04T14:02:22.992298+00:00", "messages": [{"uuid": "37cd8c34-63da-4443-a291-41ec5fd33076", "role": "user", "content": {"attachments": [{"content": "This project uses Design Components: every design is a single streaming `Name.dc.html` file. The full authoring spec is in your system prompt under \"Writing code \u2014 Design Components\" \u2014 follow it. Author and edit `.dc.html` content with the `dc_write`, `dc_html_str_replace`, `dc_js_str_replace`, and `dc_set_props` tools (not `write_file`; `str_replace_edit` works but won't stream); template edits stream into the live preview as you type.", "id": "7f443447-e4b1-46bd-8637-7942382d3702", "name": "Design Components", "type": "skill"}], "authorAccountUuid": "bf0089cd-fef6-440b-9df5-3891221a315d", "authorName": "Tom", "content": "\u7ed9 TalKo \u8bbe\u8ba1\u4e00\u4e2a\u5e94\u7528\u56fe\u6807", "id": "37cd8c34-63da-4443-a291-41ec5fd33076", "role": "user", "timestamp": "2026-07-04T13:46:18.183679967Z"}, "created_at": "2026-07-04T13:46:18.192051+00:00"}, {"uuid": "570b1064-7929-5e58-8bb3-e738f0356691", "role": "assistant", "content": {"id": "460f1e8c-ce72-4bd9-b4a2-7c24c060d26f", "role": "assistant", "content": "", "contentBlocks": [{"type": "tool_call", "toolCall": {"id": "toolu_01Qyy7a8PAe9z2Ysos2uvYmR", "type": "edit", "name": "questions_v2", "input": {"questions": [{"id": "product", "kind": "freeform", "subtitle": "\u4e00\u53e5\u8bdd\u4ecb\u7ecd\u4ea7\u54c1\u5b9a\u4f4d\u3001\u76ee\u6807\u7528\u6237", "title": "TalKo \u662f\u505a\u4ec0\u4e48\u7684\uff1f"}, {"id": "vibe", "kind": "text-options", "options": ["\u53cb\u597d\u6d3b\u6cfc\uff08\u5bf9\u8bdd\u611f\u5f3a\uff09", "\u4e13\u4e1a\u514b\u5236\uff08\u5546\u52a1/\u751f\u4ea7\u529b\uff09", "\u79d1\u6280\u672a\u6765\u611f", "\u53ef\u7231\u840c\u7cfb", "\u6781\u7b80\u51e0\u4f55", "Explore a few options", "Decide for me", "Other"], "title": "\u60f3\u8981\u7684\u6574\u4f53\u6c14\u8d28"}, {"id": "symbol", "kind": "text-options", "multi": true, "options": ["\u5b57\u6bcd T / K \u9020\u578b", "\u5bf9\u8bdd\u6c14\u6ce1", "\u58f0\u6ce2/\u8bed\u97f3", "\u62bd\u8c61\u51e0\u4f55", "\u5b57\u6bcd+\u6c14\u6ce1\u7ed3\u5408", "Explore a few options", "Decide for me", "Other"], "title": "\u56fe\u6807\u7b26\u53f7\u65b9\u5411"}, {"id": "palette", "kind": "text-options", "options": ["\u660e\u4eae\u6d3b\u529b\uff08\u6a59/\u9ec4/\u7ea2\uff09", "\u6e05\u65b0\u84dd\u7eff", "\u7d2b\u8272\u79d1\u6280", "\u9ed1\u767d\u6781\u7b80", "\u6e10\u53d8\u591a\u5f69", "Decide for me", "Other"], "title": "\u8272\u5f69\u503e\u5411"}, {"id": "shape", "kind": "svg-options", "options": ["<svg viewBox='0 0 80 56'><rect x='20' y='4' width='40' height='48' rx='10' fill='#333'/></svg>", "<svg viewBox='0 0 80 56'><rect x='20' y='4' width='40' height='48' rx='20' fill='#333'/></svg>", "<svg viewBox='0 0 80 56'><circle cx='40' cy='28' r='24' fill='#333'/></svg>"], "title": "\u56fe\u6807\u5916\u5f62\uff08iOS/Android \u5706\u89d2\u65b9\u5f62\uff09"}, {"default": 3, "id": "variants", "kind": "slider", "max": 6, "min": 1, "step": 1, "title": "\u60f3\u770b\u51e0\u4e2a\u65b9\u6848\uff1f"}, {"id": "context", "kind": "text-options", "options": ["\u5355\u4e2a\u5927\u56fe\u6807", "\u4e3b\u5c4f\u7f51\u683c\u4e2d", "App Store \u5c55\u793a", "\u5168\u90e8", "Decide for me"], "title": "\u8981\u5c55\u793a\u7684\u573a\u666f"}]}, "output": "Questions form is now displayed to the user. Inform them you've asked some questions (which should be visible on their screen in the preview pane) and end your turn. Wait for their response. If they n"}}, {"type": "thinking", "text": ""}], "timestamp": "2026-07-04T13:46:34.686Z", "turnInputTokens": 34314}, "created_at": "2026-07-04T13:46:49.532596+00:00"}, {"uuid": "45098ce8-97a0-466a-9642-1bc129c2ba63", "role": "user", "content": {"authorAccountUuid": "bf0089cd-fef6-440b-9df5-3891221a315d", "authorName": "Tom", "content": "Questions answered:\n- vibe: \u4e13\u4e1a\u514b\u5236\uff08\u5546\u52a1/\u751f\u4ea7\u529b\uff09\n- symbol: \u5b57\u6bcd+\u6c14\u6ce1\u7ed3\u5408\n- palette: \u9ed1\u767d\u6781\u7b80\n- shape: 0\n- variants: 2\n- context: \u5168\u90e8", "id": "45098ce8-97a0-466a-9642-1bc129c2ba63", "role": "user", "timestamp": "2026-07-04T13:49:39.758540612Z"}, "created_at": "2026-07-04T13:49:39.766114+00:00"}, {"uuid": "2411170b-f7d7-5b0d-86b1-cfac48c4be8d", "role": "assistant", "content": {"id": "ddaa62dc-bb62-4d23-b903-0991de758c15", "role": "assistant", "content": "", "contentBlocks": [{"type": "tool_call", "toolCall": {"id": "toolu_01V6haCA92g5Xv2EMjDuVP2g", "type": "edit", "name": "dc_write", "input": {"a_filename": "TalKo Icon.dc.html", "b_dc_html": "<helmet>\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<meta name=\"design_doc_mode\" content=\"canvas\">\n<style>\n  body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f2; color: #0a0a0a; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n</style>\n</helmet>\n\n<div style=\"padding: 64px 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 72px; min-height: 100vh;\">\n\n  <header style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #8a8a86; text-transform: uppercase;\">Turn 01 \u00b7 App Icon Exploration</div>\n      <h1 style=\"margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em;\">TalKo \u2014 Icon System</h1>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #8a8a86; text-align: right; line-height: 1.7;\">\n      Monochrome \u00b7 Letter + Speech Bubble<br>\n      2 directions \u00b7 iOS / Android / Store\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- ============ TURN 1 ============ -->\n  <section style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 40px; align-items: stretch; flex-wrap: wrap;\">\n\n    <!-- ================ OPTION 1A ================ -->\n    <div id=\"1a\" style=\"flex: 1 1 560px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e5e2; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 36px;\">\n\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;\">\n          <span style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 34px; height: 26px; padding: 0 10px; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; border-radius: 6px;\">1a</span>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\">Bubble-as-Counter</div>\n            <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #8a8a86; margin-top: 2px;\">The \"o\" is the conversation</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Hero icon -->\n      <div style=\"background: #f4f4f2; border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 320px; height: 320px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 72px; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.06) inset, 0 24px 48px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n          <!-- Wordmark: Tal -->\n          <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 132px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n            <span>Tal</span>\n            <!-- speech bubble as 'k' + 'o' -->\n            <span style=\"margin-left: 2px;\">k</span>\n            <!-- bubble replacing 'o' -->\n            <span style=\"position: relative; margin-left: 4px;\">\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 96px; height: 96px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 8px; position: relative; top: 10px;\"></span>\n            </span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Grid contexts -->\n      <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;\">\n        <!-- iOS home screen -->\n        <div style=\"background: #f4f4f2; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #8a8a86; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;\">iOS \u00b7 Home</div>\n          <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d9d5cf 0%, #b8b3ab 100%); border-radius: 22px; padding: 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px;\">\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #2a6fdb; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #34c759; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <!-- TalKo -->\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 22%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative;\">\n              <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n                <span>Tal</span><span>k</span>\n                <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 2px; margin-left: 1px; position: relative; top: 1px;\"></span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #ff9500; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #af52de; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #ff3b30; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #5ac8fa; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #ffcc00; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #4a4a46; font-weight: 500;\">TalKo</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- App Store -->\n        <div style=\"background: #f4f4f2; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #8a8a86; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;\">App Store</div>\n          <div style=\"background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;\">\n            <div style=\"width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n              <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n                <span>T</span>\n                <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 2px; margin-left: 1px;\"></span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 0;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\">TalKo</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #8a8a86; margin-top: 2px;\">Team messaging, focused.</div>\n              <div style=\"font-size: 10px; color: #8a8a86; margin-top: 6px;\">\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605\u2605 \u00b7 Productivity</div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"padding: 5px 14px; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 12px;\">GET</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Size ladder -->\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #8a8a86; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;\">Scale \u00b7 120 / 80 / 48 / 32 / 20</div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 20px;\">\n          <!-- 120 -->\n          <div style=\"width: 120px; height: 120px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 27px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 48px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n              <span>Tal</span><span>k</span>\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 34px; height: 34px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 4px; margin-left: 2px; position: relative; top: 3px;\"></span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- 80 -->\n          <div style=\"width: 80px; height: 80px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n              <span>Tal</span>\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 20px; height: 20px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 3px; margin-left: 1px; position: relative; top: 2px;\"></span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- 48 -->\n          <div style=\"width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 11px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n              <span>T</span>\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 2px; margin-left: 1px;\"></span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- 32 -->\n          <div style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 7px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n              <span>T</span>\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 1px; margin-left: 1px;\"></span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- 20 -->\n          <div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: baseline; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 1;\">\n              <span>T</span>\n              <span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 4px; height: 4px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 1px; margin-left: 0.5px;\"></span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Rationale -->\n      <div style=\"padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e2; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #4a4a46; line-height: 1.7;\">\n        <div style=\"color: #8a8a86; margin-bottom: 6px;\">// RATIONALE</div>\n        The wordmark carries the brand at large sizes; the \"o\" collapses into a chat bubble tail \u2014 legible as a monogram T + bubble at 32px and below. Keeps typographic identity intact.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- ================ OPTION 1B ================ -->\n    <div id=\"1b\" style=\"flex: 1 1 560px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e5e2; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 36px;\">\n\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;\">\n          <span style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 34px; height: 26px; padding: 0 10px; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; border-radius: 6px;\">1b</span>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\">Bubble-Container</div>\n            <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: #8a8a86; margin-top: 2px;\">Monogram inside a speech bubble</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Hero icon -->\n      <div style=\"background: #f4f4f2; border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 320px; height: 320px; background: #ffffff; border: 2px solid #0a0a0a; border-radius: 72px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 24px 48px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\">\n          <!-- speech bubble container -->\n          <div style=\"width: 220px; height: 200px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 44px; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n            <!-- Monogram TK -->\n            <div style=\"color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 108px; letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 1;\">TK</div>\n            <!-- Tail -->\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -18px; left: 40px; width: 40px; height: 40px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 0 0 6px 40px; transform: skewX(-10deg);\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Grid contexts -->\n      <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;\">\n        <!-- iOS home screen -->\n        <div style=\"background: #f4f4f2; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #8a8a86; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;\">iOS \u00b7 Home</div>\n          <div style=\"background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d9d5cf 0%, #b8b3ab 100%); border-radius: 22px; padding: 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px;\">\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #2a6fdb; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #34c759; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <!-- TalKo -->\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #0a0a0a; border-radius: 22%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative;\">\n              <div style=\"width: 68%; height: 62%; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 30%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative;\">\n                <div style=\"color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: -0.05em;\">TK</div>\n                <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 6px; width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0a0a0a; border-radius: 0 0 1px 8px; transform: skewX(-10deg);\"></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #ff9500; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #af52de; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; background: #ff3b30; border-radius: 22%;\"></div>\n         